overview: Che Weel, the villagehead of Kg. Jubakar was accused by Brahim for killing his son, Muhaimi. As a result, Che Well was hated by the villagers, this went on until he became stressed and turned into a shut-in. Zamarol, Che Well's son has also been barred from contacting his girlfriend, Norain who is also Brahim's nephew.
title: Jubakar
